<% content_for(:navbar) do %>
  <%= render 'shared/navbars/navbar_home' %>
<% end %>

<!-- Banner  -->
<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,128,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,36,51,0.4) 50%), url(<%= image_path('banner3.jpg') %>);">
  <div class="banner-float">
    <p>Brexit means lots of uncertainties...</p>
    <h4>We help you to protect your resident status. We provide you with the infrastructure of trust for the Home Office.
    </h4>
    <h4>You collect, save and deliver your proofs of presence on time.</h4>
  </div>

  <div class="banner-content zero-text-margin">

    <%= link_to new_user_session_path, class: "white-text" do %>
      <button class="btn btn-secondary white-button">Enroll now for our Beta Version</button>
    <% end %>
    <p></p>
  </div>

  <div class="banner-strip">
    <p>We will inform you as soon as we are live!</p>
    <p>Do not let other people decide for your future.</p>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- What do we do for you? -->
<section class="container text-center" id="instructions">
  <h2>What we do for you...</h2>
  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <%= image_tag('NotaUK.png', class: "feature-image") %>
      <h4>Not a UK Citizen</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">Brexit is threatening your eligibility to stay in the UK. You could lose most of your rights. We have created a unique web application to get prepared for adverse events. No delay, no missing document, no undesirable or adminstrative error possible.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <%= image_tag('Vault1.png', class: "feature-image") %>
      <h4>Protect your data and your family</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">We designate your guardians. You store your proofs of residency prior to the 23rd of June 2016. You save your will, your messages, any information and data you would like to pass to your friends and family. We use the Blockchain infrastructure for your guardian nomination authenticity and we also store your personal data through two layers of security.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
    <div class="flexbox-vertical feature">
      <%= image_tag('network1.png', class: "feature-image") %>
      <h4>A unique unlocking process</h4>
      <p class="text-justify">We follow a strict process to release your data if you decide not do it yourself. Your approvers unlock the data on the call to action you have defined. Then, we authorise guardians to access their private portal to back you up. We can deliver your proofs of residency to the Home Office directly if you want it.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- Caroussel - Medias -->

<div class="wrapper">
  <section id="media-quotes" class="container content-section text-center">
    <h2>...because you need to be ready.</h2>
    <p>European Citizens will soon not benefit from the same rights.<br>History and recent political
    events remind us we need to be prepared to protect us and our relatives.</p>

    <div id="carousel-container">
    <div class="cloud9-carousel" id="cloud9-carousel">

      <div class="cloud9-item pink-border">
        <p>“In absence of guardian nomination it can take up to 26 weeks for kids to join their relatives after their parents disappear."</p>
        <%= image_tag('Law_Society.png', class: "carousel-image") %>
      </div>

      <div class="cloud9-item purple-border">
        <p>“EU family Law and passport does not apply to UK.</p>
        <%= image_tag('European_Commission.png', class: "carousel-image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="cloud9-item aqua-border">
        <p>“Prove your right to live in the UK as an EU citizen"</p>
        <%= image_tag('logo-govuk.png', class: "carousel-image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="cloud9-item orange-border">
        <p>“EU citizens urged to collect evidence they lived in UK prior to Brexit vote"</p>
        <%= image_tag('Independent_logo.png', class: "carousel-image") %>
      </div>
      <div class="cloud9-item blue-border">
        <p>“Over 24,000 children are bereaved of a parent each year in Britain and yet very few people have chosen a legal guardian for their little ones"</p>
        <%= image_tag('telegraph_logo.png', class: "carousel-image") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<!-- Feedback -->
<section id="feedback" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,128,0.4) 0%, rgba(0,36,51,0.4) 50%), url(<%= image_path('banner2.jpg') %>);">
  <div class="container text-center" id="reviews">
    <h2>Act now!</h2>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="review-box">
          <p>“I did not have any family in the UK when my parents passed away. I was devastated by the news and completely lost. I stayed more than 20 weeks alone under British Authorities control before being allowed to join my grand-parents in Poland. My parents had not named guardians as it is something you are never asked.“</p>
          <p>Imre</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-6">
        <div class="review-box">
          <p>“When my sister had a deadly accident, she was divorced from her husband with two sons and living in the UK. My nephews have been placed in an orphanage as there was no named guardian and UK authorithies judge their father was not eligible. I finally got custody after four months and a long and painful process for them. I have myself named guardians. It should be as natural as it is for an insurance policy.“</p>
          <p>Iva</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

